ISLAMABAD, Jun 22 (APP):Minister for Foreign Affairs Bilawal Bhutto Zardari Thursday thanked the members of Asia Pacific Group at the United Nations for their support and confidence in unanimously endorsing Pakistan’s candidature to the UN Security Council for the term 2025-2026.
In a tweet the foreign minister said,”I thank the members of Asia Pacific Group at UN in NY for their support & confidence in unanimously endorsing Pakistan’s candidature to the UN Security Council for the term 2025-2026.”Pakistan was determined to make its contributions while upholding the principles of United Nations Charter, he added.
